"เพื่อสร้างระเบียน :guilabel:`ใหม่`"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:2094
msgid ""
"Select the reference :guilabel:`Year` and :guilabel:`Month`, then "
